[17.729294, "o", "Build, Download and Upload artifacts, create deploy order then deploy from artifacts\r\n\r\n\u001b[32mUsage\u001b[0m:\r\n  > artifacts {flags} <action> \r\n\r\n\u001b[32mFlags\u001b[0m:\r\n  \u001b[36m-c\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--combine\u001b[0m - Build and upload the artifact to the dest project and deploy to the dest\r\n  \u001b[36m-n\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--no-deploy\u001b[0m - Don't deploy after creating deploy order\r\n  \u001b[36m-f\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--from\u001b[0m <\u001b[94mString\u001b[0m> - Alias of source config to build or download artifact\r\n  \u001b[36m-t\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--to\u001b[0m <\u001b[94mString\u001b[0m> - Alias of destination config to upload or deploy artifact\r\n  \u001b[36m-i\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--doid\u001b[0m <\u001b[94mString\u001b[0m> - The deploy order ID to deploy and query the deploy detail\r\n  \u001b[36m-b\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--branch\u001b[0m <\u001b[94mString\u001b[0m> - The branch name to build the artifact\r\n  \u001b[36m-v\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--version\u001b[0m <\u001b[94mString\u001b[0m> - The version number of the artifact to deploy\r\n  \u001b[36m-e\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--dest-env\u001b[0m <\u001b[94mString\u001b[0m> - The dest environment to deploy the artifact, such as DEV,TEST,STAGIN"]
[17.729359, "o", "G,PROD, etc.\r\n  \u001b[36m-g\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--deploy-group\u001b[0m <\u001b[94mString\u001b[0m> - The app group to deploy for the specified artifact, `All` by default\r\n  \u001b[36m-h\u001b[39m,\u001b[0m \u001b[36m--help\u001b[0m - Display the help message for this command\r\n\r\n\u001b[32mParameters\u001b[0m:\r\n  \u001b[36maction\u001b[0m <\u001b[94mstring\u001b[0m>: Action to perform, such as `deploy`, `produce`, and `consume`\r\n\r\n\u001b[32mInput/output types\u001b[0m:\r\n   \u001b[1;32m#\u001b[0m \u001b[37m \u001b[0m \u001b[1;32minput\u001b[0m \u001b[37m \u001b[0m \u001b[1;32moutput\u001b[0m \r\n  \u001b[37m────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n   \u001b[1;32m0\u001b[0m \u001b[37m \u001b[0m \u001b[37many\u001b[0m   \u001b[37m \u001b[0m \u001b[37many\u001b[0m    \r\n\r\n\r\n"]
